xkcd-substitutions
------------------

Substitutions that make reading the news more fun!

Fetch random articles from https://www.reddit.com/r/news,
substitute them xkcd style.

Inspired from xkcd Substitutions
    1. https://xkcd.com/1004
    2. https://xkcd.com/1031
    3. https://xkcd.com/1288
    4. https://xkcd.com/1418
    5. https://xkcd.com/1625
    6. https://xkcd.com/1679


SETUP
    [+] sudo pip install -U newspaper requests
    [+] git clone https://github.com/clickyotomy/xkcd-substitutions


USAGE
    read.py [-h] [-w N] [-d [DEBUG [http, text, repl ...]]]

    Substitutions that make reading the news more fun!
    https://github.com/clickyotomy/xkcd-substitutions

    optional arguments:
      -h, --help            show this help message and exit
      -w N, --width N       text width; default: 80
      -d [DEBUG [http, text, repl ...]], --debug [DEBUG [http, text, repl ...]]
                            enable debugging; http: http-requests,
                            text: orignal-content, repl: text-replacement


NOTES
    `substitutions.json` will be updated when a new issue of the comic
    is released.
